Package com.jshobe.secrethub

The SecretHub client API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SecretHubLibrary
    SecretHubLibrary is an interface that provides the JNA mappings to the the secrethub-go native library.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client
    Client provides methods to access secrets stored in SecretHub.
    Secret
    Secret represents a decrypted secret in SecretHub.
    SecretHubLibrary.Client
    The SecretHub Client structure.
    SecretHubLibrary.Secret
    The SecretHub Secret structure.
    SecretHubLibrary.SecretVersion
    The SecretHub SecretVersion structure.
    SecretHubLibrary.SecretVersion.ByValue  
    SecretVersion
    SecretVersion represents a version of a secret without any encrypted data.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SecretHubException
    SecretHubException signals that an error occurred during a call to the SecretHub client library.
